    "body": "another possibility would be to add a new `kind` of link (like `filepath`). It could be a good compromise between unexpected-magic and code-complexity.\n\nFrom my understanding of `framework`, it wouldn't conflict as it shouldn't be expected to have a link with `framework` **and** with `filepath`. (The `-framework` option tells the linker to search for `name.frame-work/name` in the framework search path).\n",
